    "It shows good performance on the training data as it becomes more biased to the previously seen data 42.",
    "But, it fails to generalize to the unseen validation or testing data.",
    "To solve these problems posed by irrelevant features in the feature space, we use L 1 regularized SVM to make the feature space free from irrelevant features before applying the feature vector to DNN.",
