    "To validate the fact that feature selection coupled with the feature extraction capability of DNN improves the performance of DNN, in Section \"Comparative study\", we performed experiments by applying all the features to DNN, i.e., removing the feature selection SVM model and then compared it with the proposed L 1 SVM-DNN."
